{"tid":941233,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"築地市場搬去豐洲之後，有無人去過築地場外巿場？","createTime":"2018-12-14T15:19:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-15T08:22:56.000Z","uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"84f27e3f3a6b6e46a208a97bdc51a58fb36e306c","tid":941233,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T15:19:03.000Z","msg":"我從未去過築地<br />\n<br />\n睇資料築地市場搬遷之後，場外巿場仍然係原地繼續營業<br />\n<br />\n有無人知現時場外市場旺唔旺，多唔多遊客？ 值唔值得去？<br />\n<br />\n因我二月會去東京，諗緊去唔去築地場外巿場"},{"pid":"a8b4e33f531aa40f1b34857b6c63da3035579020","tid":941233,"uid":170792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T15:37:00.000Z","msg":"場外市場個拉麵次次經過好多日本人食"},{"pid":"b9570949dddbeed374faa9a337accbccd5a0666c","tid":941233,"uid":165521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a8b4e33f531aa40f1b34857b6c63da3035579020","tid":941233,"uid":170792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T15:37:00.000Z","msg":"場外市場個拉麵次次經過好多日本人食"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T15:38:11.000Z","msg":"之前唔係火災燒咗咩"},{"pid":"20c6c57002fe091089f5b4d506e7ff9283ab04e1","tid":941233,"uid":29070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T15:45:35.000Z","msg":"豊洲咪去 未成熟<br />\n場外ok"},{"pid":"412d10bdb2d0bf2f19200b8c388c5392109928ab","tid":941233,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T15:53:23.000Z","msg":"其實我想知，場外巿場會唔會比起以往少咗遊人去？ 我prefer少啲人無咁迫"},{"pid":"e1fa265949c137eaa4c029b34176392fbf79bba0","tid":941233,"uid":50801,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T04:33:52.000Z","msg":"都係迫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PzrtSbm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPzrtSbm.jpg&h=1fcc7afe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢張相係星期六上午十點左右影，已經多人到咁<br />\n去到正午食飯果陣係人貼人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n約莫有一半鋪頭冇搬，未去過不妨去迫下<br />\n<br />\n豊洲